title: Horsefly Chronicles - The Farside Paranormal Podcast Episode 6
description:
The Farside is a new Paranormal Podcast that some may have an interest in.
This episode features Phil Siracusa and his true life story of being evicted out of heaven and thrust into hell.


What would you do if a demonic entity followed you back to the earth as you reincarnated?

Other episodes may be uploaded if there is a demand for the show here.
Past episodes featured John Hogue, Frank Mares and others.

It is new but I can see a time when this could be an alternative to Coast to Coast AM with George Noory.
